beer.beer_description: This single hopped IPA is juicy, fresh, and available for a limited time only at Dan Murphy’s…so get on board! ‘Idaho-7’ has a golden hue, thanks to a blend of pale malts. Expect aromas of tangerine, white grape and candied pineapple. On the palate, stone fruit, hints of pine and a soft, moreish sweetness. If you like our Mosaic IPA, this one’ll float your boat. Pair with fried chicken and sunshine.
